{"tid":1680362,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[整理] 城大Hall10畢架嶺事件","createTime":"2019-10-28T18:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T17:31:09.000Z","uid":30836,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4973a3e5cf4a45c232e7a7b4b465fd15c68ca208","tid":1680362,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:27:48.000Z","msg":"涉事ig post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B37iNHRBIkq/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB37iNHRBIkq%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=cc8e667c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB37iNHRBIkq%2F&h=683f42c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B37iNHRBIkq/</a><br />\n<br />\n內文（點擊展開）<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hall10_tenacity<br />\n▪️畢架嶺▫️<br />\n曾經嘅兇宅，如今變成學生宿舍。當年未能破解嘅離奇命案，陰魂，到而家仍然不散。學生一個、又一個失蹤，宿舍淨低嘅...作為學生記者嘅你，又夠唔夠膽去尋找真相？<br />\n-<br />\n［Mystery Beacon Hill］萬聖節<br />\n日期：31/10<br />\n時間：19:30-23:00<br />\n地點：宿十P1全層<br />\n報名：即場報名入場<br />\n聯絡方式：草 6723 7309<br />\n-<br />\n[Mystery Beacon Hill] Halloween<br />\nPeople come. People die. Waaaaaaaaa!<br />\n-<br />\nDate: 31/10<br />\nTime: 19:30-23:00<br />\nVenue: Hall 10 P1<br />\nApplication: Walk-in<br />\nContact: Grass 6723 7309<br />\n-<br />\n-<br />\n-<br />\n#拾情<br />\n#十里<br />\n#城大宿十<br />\n#tenacity <br />\n#cityuhall10</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>相關宣傳單張</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rPMLQ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2rPMLQ6.jpg&h=46041b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>ig post宣傳影片截圖</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyeEme5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyeEme5.jpg&h=45ebe3af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48935c09370914efa7774e51faa8023952e60fad","tid":1680362,"uid":311238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score